            migration                                                           
                24      operation.                                              
                25                                                              
                26      If you attempt to insert a new row that conflicts with  
            an existing row, an                                                 
                27      :exc:`~django.db.IntegrityError` is raised. Similarly,  
            when update                                                         
                28      conflicts with an existing row.                         
                29                                                              
                30      Exclusion constraints are checked during the :ref:`model
            validation                                                          
                                                                                
                                                                                
